---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="QVault — Quantum Security & Key Distribution">
  <style>
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 8rem 2rem 6rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 800px;
      height: 800px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
      color: #00d4ff;
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .badge::before {
      content: '';
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      background: #00d4ff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.3; }
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0066cc);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #4a6fa5;
      max-width: 540px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0066cc);
      color: #050a0e;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: #e0f0ff;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      border: 1px solid #0a3a5c;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: #00d4ff; transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 4rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: #0a1628;
      border: 1px solid #0a3a5c;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: #e0f0ff;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4a6fa5;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 4rem;
      padding: 4rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #0a3a5c;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #0a3a5c;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #00d4ff;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .stat p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #4a6fa5;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="badge">Quantum Key Distribution</div>
    <h1>Unbreakable security,<br><span>quantum guaranteed</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      QVault delivers post-quantum cryptography and QKD infrastructure that protects your most critical data against both classical and quantum threats.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Request Access</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-secondary">Read Whitepaper</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <h2>256-bit</h2>
      <p>Post-quantum key strength</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h2>&lt;1ms</h2>
      <p>Key exchange latency</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h2>100%</h2>
      <p>Information-theoretic security</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h2>NIST</h2>
      <p>PQC standards compliant</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔐</div>
      <h3>Quantum Key Distribution</h3>
      <p>Leverage the laws of quantum mechanics to distribute cryptographic keys with unconditional security, making interception physically impossible.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
      <h3>Post-Quantum Cryptography</h3>
      <p>NIST-approved algorithms (CRYSTALS-Kyber, CRYSTALS-Dilithium) that remain secure against quantum computer attacks.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔗</div>
      <h3>Hybrid Security Architecture</h3>
      <p>Seamlessly combine classical and quantum cryptography layers for defense-in-depth during the quantum transition period.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Hardware Security Modules</h3>
      <p>Tamper-proof quantum HSMs for key generation, storage, and management at enterprise and government scale.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
      <h3>Network Integration</h3>
      <p>Drop-in compatibility with existing PKI infrastructure. Upgrade to quantum security without replacing your entire stack.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
      <h3>Audit & Compliance</h3>
      <p>Real-time monitoring, immutable audit logs, and compliance reporting for FIPS 140-3, CC EAL4+, and sector-specific standards.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
